1:1 COMMENT "# armpred.z - Arm predicates on variant/union instances"
1:56 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# On a VALUE of a variant or union, naming an arm is a boolean predicate:"
3:74 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# `x.a` is true when x currently holds arm a. On the TYPE it remains the"
4:73 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# construction reference (`kind.a` builds the arm). bool composes: a"
5:69 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# trailing `.false` negates a predicate, `.true` passes it through."
6:68 EOL "\n"
